eue For Number&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-indent: 0cm;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 14pt; margin-left: 10px; font-family: 宋体;\">1.</span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; margin-left: 10px; font-family: 宋体;\">影院每天上报数据一定要及时、全面、准确。数据上报的时间应在营业结束后第二天中午<span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 16px; margin-left: 10px;\">12</span>点之前，否则数据平台就会显示过时补报。长期过时补报说明数据上报不及时，影院管理存在问题，片方因此会重点关注这家影院。<span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 16px; margin-left: 10px;\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0cm; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue For Number&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-indent: 0cm;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 14pt; margin-left: 10px; font-family: 宋体;\">2.</span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; margin-left: 10px; font-family: 宋体;\">影院排片一定要使用正确的影片编码。只能在国家广电总局专资影<span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 16px; margin-left: 10px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue For Number&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; margin-left: 10px; font-family: 宋体;\">片编码网站下载正确的影片编码，并注意区分发行版本。如只有普通版本，不能使用巨幕影片编码。系列片也要注意区分正在上映的影片名称，不能使用以前影片的编码，需用最新的编码。如<span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 16px; margin-left: 10px;\">2015</span>年的电影就不能使用<span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 16px; margin-left: 10px;\">2014</span>的电影编码，以免引起数据统计的混乱。（编码网站<span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 16px; margin-left: 10px;\">http://www1.zgdypw.cn/filmIssue/findFilmHistory.html</span>）<span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 16px; margin-left: 10px;\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue For Number&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 14pt; margin-left: 10px; font-family: 宋体;\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0cm; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue For Number&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-indent: 0cm;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 14pt; margin-left: 10px; font-family: 宋体;\">3.</span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; margin-left: 10px; font-family: 宋体;\">特别要注意遵守各影片发行通知上的票价协议，影片票价按城市分类，区分最低票价。特殊节假日期间，影院多片连映的，影片票价均不能低于参加连映影片的平均票价，且不低于各影片发行通知所规定的最低票价。<span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 16px; margin-left: 10px;\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0cm; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue For Number&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-indent: 0cm;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 14pt; margin-left: 10px; font-family: 宋体;\">4.</span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; margin-left: 10px; font-family: 宋体;\">电子商务售票要严格遵循《电影管理条例》等国家有